verbose_text: The levels of TXNIP and NLRP3 were significantly decreased in the miR-20b mimic group compared with those in the scramble group, but were still increased in the miR-20b inhibitor, scramble + H 2 O 2, miR-20b mimic + H 2 O 2 and miR-20b inhibitor + H 2 O 2 groups compared with those in the scramble group (P < 0.05; XREF_FIG).
